  <name>Dure</name>
  <summary>Distributed E-commerce Platform</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Dure is a distributed e-commerce client and hosting solution that enables small shop
      owners to run e-commerce operations without traditional centralized server infrastructure.
    </p>
    <p>Core Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Identity Management with cryptographic keys and attestation</li>
      <li>Guest Front for customers (product browsing, cart, ordering)</li>
      <li>Store Front for shop owners (product listings, payments)</li>
      <li>Hosting Management (DNS, Database, Site deployment)</li>
      <li>Store Management (Products, Orders, Shipments, Accounts)</li>
      <li>Payment Integration (Portone, KakaoPay)</li>
      <li>Multi-mode operation (Server, GUI, CLI)</li>
      <li>Material3 design with egui framework</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Hosting Options:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Firebase + Firestore + Cloud SQL + Cloud Messaging</li>
      <li>Cloudflare Pages + Supabase + Realtime</li>
      <li>Google Compute Engine (GCE)</li>
      <li>Cafe24 VPS</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
